</div></div><div class="x-container max width" style="margin: 0px auto 30px;padding: 0px;"  ><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-3" style="padding: 0px;" ><img  class="x-img man x-img-circle"  src="https://masto.host/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mastodon-4.png" alt="Placeholder"><h3  class="h-custom-headline mtm h4" ><span>microblogging network</span></h3><div class="x-text"  ><p class="man">It&#8217;s a microblogging social network that brings the control back to your hands.</p>
</div><hr  class="x-gap cs-hide-xl cs-hide-lg cs-hide-md" style="margin: 40px 0 0 0;"></div><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-3" style="padding: 0px;" ><img  class="x-img man x-img-circle"  src="https://masto.host/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Elephants.png" alt="Placeholder"><h3  class="h-custom-headline mtm h4" ><span>decentralized</span></h3><div class="x-text"  ><p class="man">Each Mastodon instance is independent and anyone is free to run their own.</p>
</div><hr  class="x-gap cs-hide-xl cs-hide-lg cs-hide-md" style="margin: 40px 0 0 0;"></div><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-3" style="padding: 0px;" ><img  class="x-img man x-img-circle"  src="https://masto.host/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/birds.png" alt="Placeholder"><h3  class="h-custom-headline mtm h4" ><span>open source</span></h3><div class="x-text"  ><p class="man">Mastodon is a free, open-source development that has been crowdfunded, not financed.</p>
