</div><hr  class="x-gap cs-hide-xl cs-hide-lg cs-hide-md" style="margin: 40px 0 0 0;"></div><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-3" style="padding: 0px;" ><img  class="x-img man x-img-circle"  src="https://masto.host/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/installed.png" alt="Placeholder"><h3  class="h-custom-headline mtm h4" ><span>installation</span></h3><div class="x-text"  ><p class="man">Mastodon comes pre-installed on all Masto.host hosting plans.</p>
